VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bstd::thread\b\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:std::mutex|std::atomic|std::lock_guard|std::unique_lock|std::shared_mutex|std::condition_variable
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of threads without mutex protection, which can lead to race conditions.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Race Condition: std::thread without mutex.
